notes: Andrachne colchica is now renamed under <g>Leptopus</g>

Many plants formerly in genus Aster have been reassigned. The majority have moved into <g>Symphyotrichum</g>. Others can be found under <g>Doellingeria</g>, <g>Eurybia</g>, <g>Galatella</g> or <g>Solidago</g>
For C. maximum see L. x superbum under <g>Leucanthemum</g>
For S. arundinacea, see A. lessoniana under <g>Anemanthele</g>
